a18e33fe02e623b4e9b6caa60cb619001551d10d","tid":783730,"uid":10044,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T00:55:56.000Z","msg":"Me too<br />\n雖然無你咁嚴重<br />\n但唔知點解佢結左婚搬走左之後會咁少聯絡<br />\n生完之後仲難約乜都話唔得閒跟住依個病個個上堂<br />\n我心諗係有心都會有時間掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n幾年都無返嚟食食淨係新年會返一兩次<br />\n但奶奶個邊就個個星期返<br />\n搞到我好似個家婆咁煩住約佢 又好似搞到我為左睇bb先約佢<br />\n<br />\n有時好羨慕人地成家人感情咁好 成日一齊出街食飯<br />\n有時關係唔係你想就會直線上升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3792ac97d7e3c8c7ec09e0c841574b98ffe5da8","tid":783730,"uid":118551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T01:03:03.000Z","msg":"好多兄弟都係咁 我同阿哥都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過我諗家姐應該易啲熟絡返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66ce9ddd12c715117f06a635737e8cbe3399c701","tid":783730,"uid":40337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T01:16:56.000Z","msg":"反左面?"},{"pid":"26038e6b5a899a729ab8379ba4d0600c90bdc5f0","tid":783730,"uid":189875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5846532dc290af64bba777687b32e9824ce4e081","tid":783730,"uid":76855,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T18:35:20.000Z","msg":"其實有父母親節<br />\n<br />\n點解冇家姐細佬節<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T01:37:06.000Z","msg":"如果有愛，日日都係家姐細佬節。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBTW,點解冇兄貴妹妹節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d8904e797a81eea39de5d7eb4d4b8ef768b8860","tid":783730,"uid":189875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"356800a7ae1039fdbda4b170a6bd6a9cf8a50be1","tid":783730,"uid":76855,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e95117ad3ea955be183d7e87280ade305020255e","tid":783730,"uid":76855,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecfda4e2bb919ebed325bc7881121646d397a3fd","tid":78